data.title: Tower of Power
data.meta_description:
Our NEW photgraphs of Old Main show you the rich beauty of this Federal Style Building. Originally called “The Main Building” this was PSU’s first major building. Old Main as we now know it sits on the original footprint of “The Main Building”. Old Main was rebuilt in 1930 using some of the original limestone.

"Shadows of Old Main" is available in the following sizes: 8x10,11x14,16x20,20x24,and 24x30.

Unframed images come in a white mat and are shrink wrapped for protection. The unframed 20x24 and 24x30 prints come rolled in a tube.  Each framed image includes double mats, glass, and your choice of a black, mahogany, cherry, or walnut frame.
